{"tid":1840802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫管局：一確診新型肺炎病人情況轉差 需用氧氣機","createTime":"2020-01-25T04:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T08:07:00.000Z","uid":212626,"like":241,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"4afb7d4e012927e81e29db809512d4adb6dc10e0","tid":1840802,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:09:07.000Z","msg":"本港確診5宗新型冠狀病毒感染個案，醫管局質素及安全總監鍾健禮表示，5人目前情況總體穩定，但其中一名病人情況轉差，今早氣喘多了，開始需要使用氧氣機協助呼吸，會密切留意。<br />\n<br />\n他稱，屯門醫院在周四處理第三宗確診病人期間，由於負壓房正在使用，故安排病人在一間非負壓病房逗留3至4小時，已通報衞生防護中心，安排專家到屯門醫院了解風險，就處理上未能盡善盡美致歉。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，目前有603張負壓病床，使用量四成，325間負壓病房，使用量六成，但擔心新春假期後，壓力會非常大。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2362766/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2362766%2F&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT%2F3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=90d49c82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2362766/</a>"},{"pid":"ba50c05ef1b31f8c4ddb010c334a216a60f18c70","tid":1840802,"uid":313341,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:11:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ac1710cd3564efc9ee8cb505060c20f31dca2d0","tid":1840802,"uid":242537,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:11:59.000Z","msg":"支那送大禮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2253965a6d61bd424cd4736d8d512ee8db81a76","tid":1840802,"uid":113929,"like":79,"dislike":3,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:12:05.000Z","msg":"我好擔心部機仲用唔用得"},{"pid":"a5b934ceb5645629a1a7ea054af54eb4a04d6ae7","tid":1840802,"uid":5258,"like":54,"dislike":6,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:14:03.000Z","m